{"id":14521,"date":"2023-07-24T08:20:01","date_gmt":"2023-07-24T01:20:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=14521"},"modified":"2023-07-24T08:20:01","modified_gmt":"2023-07-24T01:20:01","slug":"kinh-nghiem-lai-xe-mua-mua-bao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/kinh-nghiem-lai-xe-mua-mua-bao\/","title":{"rendered":"KINH NGHI\u1ec6M L\u00c1I XE M\u00d9A M\u01afA B\u00c3O"},"content":{"rendered":"<div>\n<div class=\"\" dir=\"auto\">\n<div id=\":r89:\" class=\"x1iorvi4 x1pi30zi x1l90r2v x1swvt13\" data-ad-comet-preview=\"message\" data-ad-preview=\"message\">\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf xz62fqu x16ldp7u\">\n<div class=\"xu06os2 x1ok221b\">\n<div class=\"xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">KINH NGHI\u1ec6M L\u00c1I XE M\u00d9A M\u01afA B\u00c3O<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">L\u00e1i xe trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft m\u01b0a b\u00e3o ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ra ngo\u00e0i, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean l\u00e1i xe ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, do nhi\u1ec1u l\u00ed do m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i tham gia giao th\u00f4ng th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u sau khi l\u00e1i xe trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n m\u01b0a b\u00e3o<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">H\u00e3y c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng xe tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh, ki\u1ec3m tra tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng tin th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft trong nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i d\u00e0i v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00ecnh \u0111i qua thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc, \u00f9n t\u1eafc. H\u00e3y t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a m\u01b0a b\u00e3o \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111i tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p m\u01b0a b\u00e3o th\u00ec h\u00e3y l\u01b0u \u00fd nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf phanh g\u1ea5p<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Tr\u1eddi m\u01b0a l\u1edbn l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i x\u1ebf d\u00f9 c\u1ea7n g\u1ea1t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c h\u1ebft c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng x\u1ea5u x\u1ea3y ra, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e1i xe, l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng phanh g\u1ea5p b\u1edfi khi tr\u1eddi m\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t tr\u01a1n, d\u1ec5 tr\u01b0\u1ee3t khi phanh g\u1ea5p.<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111i g\u1ea7n c\u00e1c xe t\u1ea3i tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Nh\u1eefng v\u0169ng n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u1ea1t l\u00ean xe g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn khi l\u00e1i, nh\u1eefng b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n s\u1ebd b\u00e1m l\u1ea1i khi n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean v\u01b0\u1ee3t xe t\u1ea3i l\u1edbn khi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m.<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Gi\u1eef t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">M\u1ed9t k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng l\u00e1i xe b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n xe v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 th\u1ea5p khi di chuy\u1ec3n d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1eddi m\u01b0a, b\u1edfi khi ch\u1ea1y s\u1ed1 th\u1ea5p th\u00ec l\u1ef1c k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a xe s\u1ebd cao v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i v\u1eadt tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u1ed1ng x\u1ea3 khi\u1ebfn xe ch\u1ebft m\u00e1y gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean m\u1edf c\u1eeda xe khi m\u1ef1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1eadp l\u1edbn<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1eadp, m\u1ee9c n\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 c\u1eeda b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean m\u1edf c\u1eeda xe, khi m\u1edf c\u1eeda xe th\u00ec n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9a v\u00e0o, r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 h\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 xe v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong xe.<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">H\u00e3y l\u01b0u s\u1ed1 c\u1ee9u h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ecdi khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">H\u00e3y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 n\u01a1i c\u1ee9u h\u1ed9 cho xe uy t\u00edn v\u00e0 l\u01b0u s\u1ed1 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 khi x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ea5p b\u00e1ch th\u00ec h\u00e3y g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee9u h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">______________________<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">HYUNDAI H\u1ea2I PH\u00d2NG<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">&#8211; Hotline: 0906.026.299<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">&#8211; Showroom 3s: 742 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh, L\u00ea Ch\u00e2n, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">&#8211; Showroom 1s: 9\/10B L\u00ea H\u1ed3ng Ph\u00f2ng, H\u1ea3i An, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\":r8a:\" class=\"x1n2onr6\">\n<div class=\"x1n2onr6\">\n<div class=\"x6s0dn4 x1jx94hy x78zum5 xdt5ytf x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6 xh8yej3\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"xqtp20y x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6\">\n<div class=\"x10l6tqk x13vifvy\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"x1ey2m1c xds687c x5yr21d x10l6tqk x17qophe x13vifvy xh8yej3 xl1xv1r\" src=\"https:\/\/scontent.fhph1-3.fna.fbcdn.net\/v\/t39.30808-6\/362231579_1028760161505004_8374658892631874793_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_p180x540&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=k34LGmJrygYAX-q92-3&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhph1-3.fna&amp;oh=00_AfBfV4eRgYOpIj3XzqlUe_v2u7jfkE6aAgbGtbAEXqfgpA&amp;oe=64C36A7E\" alt=\"C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 xe jeep\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"xua58t2 xzg4506 x1ey2m1c xds687c x47corl x10l6tqk x17qophe x13vifvy\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"x1o1ewxj x3x9cwd x1e5q0jg x13rtm0m x1ey2m1c xds687c xg01cxk x47corl x10l6tqk x17qophe x13vifvy x1ebt8du x19991ni x1dhq9h\" data-visualcompletion=\"ignore\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x6ikm8r x10wlt62\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x8gbvx8 xdppsyt x1n2xptk x78zum5 x1q0g3np x1qughib xz9dl7a xn6708d xsag5q8 xpkgp8e\">\n<div class=\"x6s0dn4 x78zum5 x1nhvcw1\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"x168nmei x13lgxp2 x30kzoy x9jhf4c x6ikm8r x10wlt62\" data-visualcompletion=\"ignore-dynamic\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"x1n2onr6\">\n<div class=\"x6s0dn4 xi81zsa x78zum5 x6prxxf x13a6bvl xvq8zen xdj266r xktsk01 xat24cr x1d52u69 x889kno x4uap5 x1a8lsjc xkhd6sd xdppsyt\">\n<div class=\"x9f619 x1n2onr6 x1ja2u2z x78zum5 x2lah0s x1qughib x1qjc9v5 xozqiw3 x1q0g3np xykv574 xbmpl8g x4cne27 xifccgj\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt"